{
  "stem": "5795.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] They had the Rabbi Cohen of Sheffield, of blessed memory, as a relation of these balebatim who wanted somebody else in Hendon-- told him, get Hardman appointed quickly.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Apparently, this sort of maneuver was known to Mr.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Kosman, ?] alav hashalom, the warden of Hendon, who wanted me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he said, I'm hearing rumors that you're going to Sheffield.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Kosman, ?] do me a favor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I'm working for Hendon.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Unless you hear from my mouth-- not even a recording, my mouth-- don't believe anything you read or hear.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But the is like the Bible to some people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It's written in the",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I arrived-- the week before, in Sheffield, I spoke.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I said I was ready, under certain conditions, to accept Sheffield because the Hendon job had not come up yet.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And apparently-- this is Monday night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The people in Sheffield were told by certain people in Hendon, get it through the It should appear on Friday morning that Hardman has got the job at Sheffield.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Kosman-- ?] see, in Leeds, we don't get the before Saturday morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In London, you get it Friday morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when he reads this, he goes, mashugana.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He phones me up 9 o'clock Friday morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, Joe, do me a favor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I've told you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't know what's cooking around here, but lest you hear it from me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Right, then, in that case, send a disclaimer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I immediately wrote a letter to the editor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He phones me up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm not publishing it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For your sake.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You're in the middle of a very tough crowd here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you're a young man.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
